## 2. Project Mission

| Field | Statement |
|-------|-----------|
| **Platform** | Open, modular automotive electronics for custom and motorsport vehicles |
| **Gen1 objective** | Simplify BMW E30 race wiring; central DCC hub for power, logic, diagnostics |
| **Long-term** | Engineers add modules (e.g. ABS) via documented interfaces without informal architecture knowledge |

Platform behaviour shall **not** hardcode E30 specifics outside `config/vehicles/`.

