## 5. Authority Levels

When sources conflict, resolve in this order:

1. Current **work package / task** (explicit scope and constraints)
2. Approved **SRS** and requirements (`docs/SRS/`, requirement IDs)
3. **`docs/001`** System Architecture
4. **`docs/004`** Communication Protocol, **`docs/005`** Configuration Model
5. **`docs/003`** ECU Architecture (ECU boundary)
6. **`docs/ADR/`** and **`docs/EDL/`** decision records
7. **DCC internal docs** (`docs/DCC/`) for logical module policy
8. **Existing implementation** (lowest — does not override approved architecture)

Do **not** resolve contradictions silently. Escalate per §11.

Operational context (non-normative): `.ai/project_context.md`.

