## 9. Architecture Protection

The following shall **not** be modified by Implementation work without approved ADR/EDL:

- DCC three-board structure (Logic, Power, Radio)
- ECU/DCC responsibility split
- Gen1 single CAN FD topology
- DCPI binary SPI (no JSON on SPI)
- VCM ownership on DCC
- Fail-safe OFF default for power channels
- Configuration-driven vehicle behaviour

Implementation documents **describe** architecture; they do not **redefine** it.

Protected references: `docs/001`, `docs/002`, `docs/003`, `docs/DCC/DCC_Internal_Architecture.md`.

